# === Mobile app environment ===
# Backend API URL (brez /api končnice — socket.config ga doda sam).
# Expo public env var-i se morajo začeti z EXPO_PUBLIC_ da so dostopni v app.
#
# Development (lokalni backend):
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
#
# Produkcija (deployan backend):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://tastystation-bg.vercel.app/api
#
# Za EAS build: nastavi v eas.json > build.<profile>.env ali EAS Environment Variables.
